-- MOVES-Lazard names Greenhill exec Hoyle as MD, financial advisory
-- 
-- Wed Sep 03, 2014 07:59AM EDT
-- None



Sept 3 (Reuters) - Financial adviser and asset manager Lazard Ltd <LAZ.N> named Richard Hoyle as a managing director of financial advisory.

Hoyle comes from Greenhill & Co Inc <GHL.N>, where he was a managing director in its London office.